{"_path":"/maps/_visual/visualization","_dir":"_visual","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"可视化","description":"可视化是一种通过图表、图形、地图等视觉元素来传达信息的方式。可视化技术是一种将数据转换为可视化图形的技术，是数据分析的重要手段之一。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"技术"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"技术"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"模糊效果的实现"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模糊效果的实现"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"aspect-ratio","props":{"h":"503px","placeholder":"TODO - <Article-G210206-BlurStandards />"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果打不开的话 P5.js 官网有个简单的示例："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://editor.p5js.org/p5/sketches/Image:_Blur","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://editor.p5js.org/p5/sketches/Image:_Blur"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原理非常简单，模糊后的像素的颜色由它旁边一些像素点的颜色决定。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我这里使用的是最简单的计算方法，一个点的值由其相邻的八个像素点的值决定："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"x-1"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"x"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"x+1"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"y-1"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"y"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"0"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"y+1"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1/8"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们把某个像素点 (x,y) 附近的八个像素的值代入这个 3x3 表格中与乘积之和，得到的结果，就是模糊后应得的值。这个 3x3 表格也叫掩膜（Mask）。有一种类似原理的算法你们应该听过，叫做“高斯模糊”，只不过高斯模糊的掩膜的权重分配使用了高斯的正态分布函数。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"高斯模糊的原理是什么怎样在界面中实现"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"link","props":{"type":"h5","source":"https://www.zhihu.com/question/54918332/answer/142137732"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"《高斯模糊的原理是什么，怎样在界面中实现？》"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"此回答介绍了高斯模糊算法中的一些优化点："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以使用两个一维高斯滤波替代二维滤波减少运算量"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以使用查表法优化"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概念"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概念"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"视错觉的形成原理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"视错觉的形成原理？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神经科学告诉我们，注意力更像一层滤网，而不是探照灯。视觉（包括其它知觉）的形成并不是因为人被动的接受信息（感觉），而是外界信息传入后，脑内负责记忆、情感的神经网络主动参与到信息的解释中来。这也就意味着眼睛看到事物其实包含了两个阶段：一是物体发射或反射出的光进入眼睛，在视网膜上成像；二是光信号被视网膜上的细胞捕捉后，经由视觉神经网络传入大脑，大脑再对这些信号进行判断和解读 "},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-theory","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-theory"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"观看从一开始就是有选择的，眼睛对样本做出什么反应，取决于许多生理与心理因素。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"name","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"贡布里希"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"物理性错视：色彩的膨胀感、进退感、冷暖感、轻重感。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由于眼球的上、下运动比左、右运动困难，因而容易疲倦 ；因为疲倦 ，也就觉得上下的距离要比左右的更长了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将两条长短相等的直线垂直摆放，垂线要比水平线略显得略长。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"徒手画个正方形，是个横向扁长的长方形；标准的正方形倒是看起来竖向扁长。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神经信号的传递并不是像机械电路般“一电到底”：信号在神经细胞传递是依靠生物电，但在神经细胞间的传递则需要依靠物理系统的突触结构。突出结构间产生的物质并不一定会被即刻销毁，所以兴奋的神经网络会产生痕迹效应，也就导致了视觉残像。同时，因为神经细胞兴奋会引起“疲劳”，所以对响应的色彩敏感度也会降低，这导致了补色残像的发生。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"错觉的分类："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"角度或方向的错视"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分割的错视"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对比的错视"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"垂直水平的错视"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上方距离过大错视"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"反转性实体错视"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"错视图形的作用可以总结为：增强艺术作品的感染力，增强画面趣味性，增强画面空间想象；其表现手法则大致可分为：图底反转、矛盾空间、图形同构 "},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-express-methods","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-express-methods"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人们在观察一个图形时，我们的视知觉往往会把包围且封闭的部分归结为图，而把未包围的部分看成底，部分情况下也有把大面积的部分看为底，积的部分看为图 "},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-reversal-theory","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-reversal-theory"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"矛盾空间的形成原因是图案违反了现实的透视原理。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同构图形即将事物转化成一种新的形象。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"className":["sr-only"],"id":"footnote-label"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Footnotes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-theory"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.zhihu.com/xen/market/pdf-view/paid_magazine/1395853043884298240"